{
  "stem": "15694.5",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we noticed that we were not going east.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So in one way, we were glad about it, because east was unknown.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You never heard anything about it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "On the other hand, we were thinking, maybe if we did go east, we'd join Mother and Sister.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we're in two minds whether to be glad or not glad.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Anyway, before long the journey was finished, and we ended in the famous-- or the infamous-- camp of Krakau-Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Forced labor camp Krakau-Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[GERMAN], Krakau-Plaszow.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the very first day, we learned that the commandant of this camp, which is the camp where Schindler got his people from, boasted that he had killed 80,000 people with his own hand.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Boasted that he was the biggest murderer of all time and he had killed 80,000 people with his own hand.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Something to look forward to.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, we went into that camp, we had to stand in line.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Three-- what I believe were Ukrainians-- were walking up and down in front of us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They didn't like-- they had each one with a rifle, but it didn't look like shooting us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They wouldn't have brought us there to shoot us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well, maybe.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I will say all sort of thoughts went through my mind, but why are we waiting?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And amongst the few valuables we still had, I had a pocket watch.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Neither silver nor gold, but a watch at that time was already something enormous.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I took it on its chain, and I sort of swung it, and as the-- one of the Ukrainians came near, I said, what are you waiting for?",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he said, delousing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Not ready yet.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And before he said it, he-- he took a-- took a split second-- the watch was in his pocket already.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
